application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description: Demolition of up to 1,037 residential units, refurbishment of up to 960 residential units and the construction of up to 2,422 residential units, an elderly extra care facility of up to 51 units (Class C2 and a community hub (sui generis uses) and buildings falling within Classes A1/A2/A3/A4 & A5 (up to 2,289 m2), B1a & c up to 2,500m2) and a library, crches, nurseries, a new primary school, a community hall, gym, youth centre, health centre, elderly support facility and a sports hall) (up to 8,039 m2),sui generis uses the provision of a Local Park, pocket parks and other public open space, play facilities, hard and soft landscaping and public realm improvements, Energy networks and centres and renewable energy technologies.
